item.title: First youtube song
item.dc:creator: @Ruby_Forums_Coder Ruby
item.description:
@Ruby_Forums_Coder wrote:

Work on your breathing and you’ll be pretty good. It also sounds like you’re reading the lyrics from paper, work on learning the lyrics before you make songs, it flows a lot easier that way. Also, during the time you’re rapping there’s a void where the bass guitar should be playing in the background, stick that back in there. It gives the song a bit of depth rather than just a synth and snare.

You also gotta get a better mic mate, yours is so flat. Good job though. Also, wrong board, should’ve been in reviews.
